		</summary>			
	</docu>	
~]]></Comment><ReturnType Namespace="TcoCore">ITcoContext</ReturnType><ReturnBitSize>64</ReturnBitSize><Local><Name>Context</Name><Type Namespace="TcoCore">ITcoContext</Type><BitSize>64</BitSize></Local><Properties><Property><Name>property</Name></Property></Properties></Method><Method><Name>__getMessenger</Name><Comment><![CDATA[~
