			<note type="important">
				 `SymbolPath` can only contain string of 255 characters.			
			</note>
			<note type="tip">
				 This block is partially extended by IVF to provide more information about the symbol.			
			</note>
		</summary>				
	</docu>	
~]]></Comment><BitSize>2176</BitSize><SubItem><Name>SymbolPath</Name><Type>STRING(255)</Type><BitSize>2048</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs></SubItem><Method><Name>GetSignalInfo</Name><Comment><![CDATA[~
